title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Youre willing to assert your boundaries and speak up if someone transgresses them today. You may even welcome opportunities to protect and defend whats yours. But you might move so fast that you only see the world through a defensive lens rather than taking full stock of someones motivations. Perhaps you rely more on anger than on tact and patience to get you through a situation while the Libra Moon joins confrontational Mars in your 1st House of Identity. Before you cut someone off, be sure to do a double take to make certain your judgement is as wise as it is swift. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
